<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50 to-white dark:from-zinc-900 dark:to-zinc-950 py-16">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50"><%= @tagline %></h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300"><%= @subtitle %></p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-3">
      <%= link_to @primary_cta[:label], @primary_cta[:href],
                  class: "inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-500" %>
      <%= link_to @secondary_cta[:label], @secondary_cta[:href],
                  class: "inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 dark:border-zinc-600 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-5xl grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 px-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">체크리스트</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">권리·명도·세무 누락 항목 자동 감지</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">AI 권리분석</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">PDF 업로드 → 등기부 타임라인 시각화</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">명도 시뮬레이터</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">점유자 유형별 단계·비용·기간 추정</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
